  <div class="container"><!--Cart-->
    <div class="helpbox" style="background-color: #fff;padding: 30px 0px 0px;">
      <h1 style="text-align: center; color:#FFB03B; font-family: Satisfy, sans-serif;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1><br>
    </div>

    <button class="accordion">User guide for application</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p><ul>
         <li>Only users who have BMSCE email ids can login to the application</li>
         <li>New users have to register first to use the application</li>
         <li>If an order is canceled and the payment is done online then the amount will be credited into credits of the particular user</li>
         <li>Two options have been given for payment: online and credit</li>
         <li>Users can provide us feedback regarding the application or the cafeteria service using the feedback form</li>
         <li>The Menu page will guide user to order food according to their choice</li>
       </ul></p>
      </div>

    <button class="accordion">Can anyone use the application?</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p>This website is built for BMSCE college campus students and teachers. Users having a BMSCE mail id can register and login to the application and order their meal.</p>
      </div>
    
      <button class="accordion">If I want to cancel my order, within what time can I cancel the order?</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p>You can cancel the order within <b>5 minutes</b> of placing the order. 
         If the money was paid online, then money will be added into the user account in the form of credit which can be used to pay for future orders.
       </p>
      </div>
      
      <button class="accordion">Can I provide feedback about the application?</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p>Yes, kindly visit the contact section to provide feedback.</p>
      </div>

      <button class="accordion">Can I edit my order?</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p>Unfortunately, once the order has been placed successfully, you cannot edit your order. You can cancel your order within 5 minutes and place a different order, but some canellation charges will apply.</p>
      </div>

      <button class="accordion">Can we apply coupons while ordering?</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p>As of now, we do not provide any facility to apply coupons.</p>
      </div>

      <button class="accordion">Will Namma Cafeteria will be accountable for quality/quantity?</button>
      <div class="panel">
        <br>
       <p>Quality and quantity is Cafeteria responsibilty. However in case of issues with the quality or quantity, kindly submit your feedback in the contact page and we will pass it on to the cafeteria</p>
      </div>

  </div>
